OL,3,CEmpty streets and sirens: The
OL,4,Crealities of reporting Iran's
OL,5,Cretaliatory strikes
OL,7,FAs tensions rose in the Middle East
OL,8,Flast week, I'd had a flight booked to
OL,9,Fleave London on Friday night and to
OL,10,Farrive into Tel Aviv on Saturday
OL,11,Fmorning.
OL,13,FSenior International Correspondent,
OL,14,FJohn Irvine and camera operator Sean
OL,15,FSwan are permanently based in Tel
OL,16,FAviv, and I was heading there
OL,17,Fpreemptively in the case of any
OL,18,Fstrikes on Iran, to support our
OL,19,Fnewsgathering operations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
