PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772679804
OL,3,CEmpty streets and sirens: The
OL,4,Crealities of reporting Iran's
OL,5,Cretaliatory strikes
OL,7,FBack in London we'd watched closely
OL,8,Fall week as negotiations and talks
OL,9,Fwere underway in Oman, between the US
OL,10,Fand Iran.
OL,12,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio was
OL,13,Fsupposed to be in Israel on Saturday,
OL,14,Fand then during the week the visit was
OL,15,Frearranged to the following Monday -
OL,16,Fso it was decided that I'd be in place
OL,17,Fover the weekend ahead of the visit,
OL,18,Fmore talks and potentially even
OL,19,Fstrikes on Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772679804
OL,3,CEmpty streets and sirens: The
OL,4,Crealities of reporting Iran's
OL,5,Cretaliatory strikes
OL,7,FAs I landed at Ben Gurion airport in
OL,8,FTel Aviv around 05:00 on Saturday
OL,9,Fmorning, it felt similar to any other
OL,10,Ftime I'd arrived.
OL,12,FMy driver was waiting for me to take
OL,13,Fme to my hotel and in the car he said
OL,14,F"hopefully war will not start while
OL,15,Fyou are here, we have seen enough war."
OL,17,FThat optimism lasted for all of two
OL,18,Fhours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
