CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772679804
OL,3,CEmpty streets and sirens: The
OL,4,Crealities of reporting Iran's
OL,5,Cretaliatory strikes
OL,7,FI was awoken by a siren coming from my
OL,8,Fphone, with a notification which read:
OL,9,F"Due to the detection of missile
OL,10,Flaunches, alerts may be activated in
OL,11,Fthe coming minutes."
OL,13,FWhile I was sleeping, Israel and the
OL,14,FUS had struck Iran, and as we now know
OL,15,Fkilled Ayatollah Ali Khamenei.
OL,17,FMinutes later, the air raid sirens
OL,18,Fsounded out across Tel Aviv and people
OL,19,Fran for shelter - Iran was striking
OL,20,Fback.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
