CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772679804
OL,3,CEmpty streets and sirens: The
OL,4,Crealities of reporting Iran's
OL,5,Cretaliatory strikes
OL,7,FSirens alerting people to potential
OL,8,Fincoming missiles were heard in Tel
OL,9,FAviv.
OL,11,FI met up with the rest of the ITV News
OL,12,Fteam at our cameraman, Sean Swan's
OL,13,Fhouse, which has a 360-degree view
OL,14,Fover Tel Aviv. This is sadly not the
OL,15,Ffirst time the team has reported war
OL,16,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
