CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772679804
OL,3,CEmpty streets and sirens: The
OL,4,Crealities of reporting Iran's
OL,5,Cretaliatory strikes
OL,7,FOver the course of the afternoon, the
OL,8,Falerts, air raid sirens, missile
OL,9,Fstrikes and interceptions intensified,
OL,10,Fand with each one we went to the roof,
OL,11,Fput on protective equipment and
OL,12,Fcaptured each one.
OL,14,FThe biggest attack and defence
OL,15,Fhappened just as we were about to come
OL,16,Fon air for the Evening News.
OL,18,FFrom ITV News' camera position on the
OL,19,Froof, missiles and interceptions could
OL,20,Fbe seen across Tel Aviv.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772679804
OL,3,CEmpty streets and sirens: The
OL,4,Crealities of reporting Iran's
OL,5,Cretaliatory strikes
OL,7,FAround 85% of missiles aimed at Tel
OL,8,FAviv are intercepted, but some do
OL,9,Fmanage to get through.
OL,11,FIt was in the middle of the night
OL,12,Fwhen, once again, the alerts sounded
OL,13,Fand Sean rushed from bed up to his
OL,14,Froof to set the cameras rolling.
OL,16,FYou can see in the video below the
OL,17,Fincoming Iranian missile being hunted
OL,18,Fby two Israeli interceptors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772679804
OL,3,CEmpty streets and sirens: The
OL,4,Crealities of reporting Iran's
OL,5,Cretaliatory strikes
OL,7,FThe two interceptors swoop around and
OL,8,Flock on to their target, but miss. The
OL,9,Fmissile slams into central Tel Aviv.
OL,11,FTwo Israeli interceptors attempted to
OL,12,Fstop an incoming strike but missed
OL,13,Ftheir target.
OL,15,FA 40-year-old woman became the first
OL,16,FIsraeli victim of this latest war.
OL,18,FBut Israel has prepared as much as it
OL,19,Fcan in the event of war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
