OL,3,CEmpty streets and sirens: The
OL,4,Crealities of reporting Iran's
OL,5,Cretaliatory strikes
OL,7,FOn Monday, we visited the Rabin
OL,8,FMedical Centre where they had moved
OL,9,Fall hospital operations underground -
OL,10,Fpatients, beds, machines, operating
OL,11,Ftheatres, all in under two hours, on
OL,12,FSaturday night.
OL,14,FIt took less than two hours for the
OL,15,FRabin Medical Centre to move its
OL,16,Foperations underground.
OL,18,FA senior nurse there told us: "We made
OL,19,Fsure we have everything we need, we
OL,20,Fcan stay an unlimited time but I hope
OL,21,Fit's not going to last forever."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772679804
OL,3,CEmpty streets and sirens: The
OL,4,Crealities of reporting Iran's
OL,5,Cretaliatory strikes
OL,7,FThe mood in Tel Aviv reflects that
OL,8,Fsentiment. The streets are quiet, the
OL,9,Fbars and restaurants are closed.
OL,11,FThe hotel in which I'm staying is
OL,12,Fusually hugely popular, but the
OL,13,Fmanager told me today it is at 20%
OL,14,Foccupancy. I've met many of those
OL,15,Foccupants in the bomb shelter as
OL,16,Fsirens sound.
OL,18,FIt is one thing heading to a country
OL,19,Fto report on war, but completely
OL,20,Fdifferent for people who live here and
OL,21,Fhave no choice in the matter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
